sentences: She played drums for Sparks from 1997 to 2009  and contributed to BBC Radio 6 Music's This Town Ain't Big Enough For Both Of Us: The Story Of Sparks presented by Mark Radcliffe.

She was the VP of Production for Comedy Central from 2007-2011, the Senior Vice President of Production for FremantleMedia and is currently the Vice President of Production for TBS, part of Turner Broadcasting System.
